data.description: Stop! Look at this cozy 4 bedroom 2 bath home! This home is located in a neighborhood with many shopping options and schools near by. This is a great opportunity for a family to make their home. The property has enough room for a possible ADU for family or to build as an investment opportunity. Look no further easy access to the 10 freeway nestled in a nice neighborhood. The property has block wall all around and wrought iron fence in the front. This is a must see property!
